  "detailed_description": "Welcome to <strong>Pigskin Punter!</strong> A short, sweet, and <strong>silly</strong> game about getting your football through the uprights of the goal post. All while some <strong>smooth</strong> music plays in the background. There are 12 levels, each one increasing in difficulty. <strong>Can you beat them all?</strong><br><br>Aim your football with the<strong> mouse</strong>, and then time your launch! When you're ready, hit the <strong>spacebar</strong> to let it rip! <br><br><strong>I can already hear the crowd cheering you on!</strong>",
